{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019/10/fix-gatsby-link-active-class/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"21440c59-7801-5263-a3b9-e89c30eb4aeb","html":"<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<h2 id=\"2020-03-10-更新\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2020-03-10-%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" aria-label=\"2020 03 10 更新 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2020-03-10 更新：</h2>\n<p>该问题在 Gatsby v2.19.32 已修正，<a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/pull/21171\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">pull request #21171</a> 已对 reach-router 更新，解决该问题。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Gatsby <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/gatsby-link/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"language-text\">Link</code></a> 组件在检查当前激活时，没有对当前 href 转义（encodeURI），导致链接中包含中文字符时判断不准确，activeClass 无效问题。其他非拉丁字符应该都有这个问题。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/36e56/featured_media.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/5ed05/featured_media.webp 190w,\n/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/9d76b/featured_media.webp 380w,\n/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/33466/featured_media.webp 760w,\n/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/e8af0/featured_media.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/253c6/featured_media.png 190w,\n/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/810ee/featured_media.png 380w,\n/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/b4918/featured_media.png 760w,\n/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/36e56/featured_media.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/b4918/featured_media.png\"\n            alt=\"featured media\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>该问题实际是包 <a href=\"https://github.com/reach/router\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">@reach/router</a> 导致的，并已在<a href=\"https://github.com/reach/router/commit/137a1ae931d62afe1e1bb0f6180ad9347baacb4c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">这次 commit</a> 中解决，并更新 npm 为 <code class=\"language-text\">1.3.0-beta.0</code>。</p>\n<p>不过当前 Gatsby 依赖的 <code class=\"language-text\">@reach/router</code> 版本是 1.2.1，该版本<strong>未包含</strong>此 bug 修正。</p>\n<h2 id=\"临时解决\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3\" aria-label=\"临时解决 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>临时解决</h2>\n<p>当初我提了 <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/18597\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">issues</a> 和 <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/pull/18600\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">PR</a>，结果<a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/pull/18600#event-2709702550\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">找错了</a>问题根本所在 😂。随后用户 <code class=\"language-text\">pieh</code> 给出了<a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/pull/18600#issuecomment-541575112\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">临时解决方案</a>。</p>\n<p>使用 <a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com/lang/en/docs/selective-version-resolutions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Yarn resolutions</a> 配置，在 <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> 中添加如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">  <span class=\"token property\">\"resolutions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"@reach/router\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1.3.0-beta.0\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"版本\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC\" aria-label=\"版本 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>版本</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>gatsby: 2.15.36</li>\n<li>gatsby-link: 2.2.20</li>\n</ul>\n<p>等 Gatsby 的依赖更新了，要记得去掉这个临时配置。感谢热心 ❤ 的<strong>了不起的盖茨比</strong>社区成员。</p>","excerpt":"","fields":{"slug":"/2019/10/fix-gatsby-link-active-class","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/gatsby/","/tag/blog/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"临时解决 Gatsby 中文链接 activeClass 无效问题","date":"2019-10-18T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":"Gatsby Link 组件在检查当前激活时，没有对当前 href 转义，导致链接中包含中文字符时判断不准确，activeClass 无效问题。","tags":["Gatsby","blog"],"slug":"/2019/10/fix-gatsby-link-active-class","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/ed3fb/featured_media.png","srcSet":"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/ed3fb/featured_media.png 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d086ef354137ae597e613b7f47b26cbb/e7773/featured_media.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}}},"prevPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/10/food-price-increase"},"frontmatter":{"title":"武汉物价飞涨早点吃不起了"}},"nextPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/11/building-an-encrypted-messenger-with-javascript"},"frontmatter":{"title":"在 Javascript 中使用公钥加密的介绍"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019/10/fix-gatsby-link-active-class","prevPostSlug":"/2019/10/food-price-increase","nextPostSlug":"/2019/11/building-an-encrypted-messenger-with-javascript"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}